<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>⦗١٨٤⦘<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>لَهِيعَةَ ، عَنِ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/1314">‌الْحَجَّاجِ بْنِ شَدَّادٍ </a>، عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/2390">‌أَبِي صَالِحٍ الْغِفَارِيِّ، </a>عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/4500">‌عَلِيٍّ </a>بِمَعْنَى سُلَيْمَانَ بْنِ دَاوُدَ،<span class="c5"> قَالَ:</span> <span class="c2">(فَلَمَّا خَرَجَ)</span> مَكَانَ <span class="c2">(فَلَمَّا بَرَزَ)</span>.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>